<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.7.5">
<l>vēṭār tiruvēṅ kaṭammē yaviḷakkē</l>
<l>nāṭār pukaḻvē tiyarmaṉ ṉiyanāṅkūr</l>
<l>cēṭār poḻilcūḻ tiruveḷ ḷakkuḷattāy</l>
<l>pāṭā varuvēṉ viṇaiyā yiṉapāṟṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lamp which dwells in divine Vēṅkaṭam filled with hunters,</l>
<l>You of Tiruveḷḷakkuḷam, encircled by beautiful groves</l>
<l>In Nāṅkūr where dwell Vedic experts whose fame spreads through the land,</l>
<l>Remove those things which have evolved as deeds from me</l>
<l rend="indent">who comes singing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
